      <hedline>
        <hl1>On a Sunday in October, We Are at War</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mizgon Zahir letter says Afghan-Americans mourn both for Afghanistan and United States, their safe haven, as US attacks Taliban in war on terrorism; drawing</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
